WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.560 --> 00:00:07.900
Jilini.

2
00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:08.640
What?

3
00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:11.820
From now on, at home, you

4
00:00:11.820 --> 00:00:13.160
will wear this cheongsam.

5
00:00:14.420 --> 00:00:16.340
You can't outrun it, and you can't fight it.

6
00:00:17.020 --> 00:00:18.780
Forget it, it's better than those

7
00:00:18.780 --> 00:00:19.480
flimsy things

8
00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:21.300
in the room.

9
00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:22.560
Okay.

10
00:00:24.380 --> 00:00:26.240
Sir, lunch is ready.

11
00:00:28.260 --> 00:00:29.020
Can you walk by yourself?

12
00:00:29.540 --> 00:00:30.260
Where to?

13
00:00:31.360 --> 00:00:32.500
To eat.

14
00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:33.600
What else?

15
00:00:36.420 --> 00:00:38.860
I... I'm sorry,

16
00:00:40.040 --> 00:00:43.700
I want to take a shower first.

17
00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:47.660
Jilini, if you want to catch me,

18
00:00:48.060 --> 00:00:50.980
you can catch me when we're in bed.

